description: One of the most coveted locations in Loring Heights—tucked away on a quiet dead-end street just feet away from the neighborhood park and playground. This beautifully renovated 3 bed/2 bath home offers a spacious walk-out backyard, perfect for outdoor living and entertaining. Truly turnkey, it features high-end updates, including 13 triple-pane windows replaced in 2022. The backyard shed provides ideal storage or the potential for a creative flex space. Loring Heights remains one of Atlanta’s most desirable neighborhoods thanks to its unbeatable location with easy access to both Buckhead and Midtown, convenient proximity to major interstates, and direct connectivity to the expanding Northwest Beltline trail.
